be.docarch.odt2braille
Class ListStyleProperties

java.lang.Object
  be.docarch.odt2braille.ListStyleProperties

public class ListStyleProperties
extends java.lang.Object

The numbering properties of either an OpenOffice.org list or the sequence of OpenOffice.org headings. These properties are

  • styleName: the name of the numbering style.
  • numFormat: the format of the number for various levels (level 1 - level 10). Possible values are: "bullet", "" (empty string), "i", "I", "a", "A", etc.
  • prefix: the prefix of the number for various levels.
  • suffix: the suffix of the number for various levels.
  • displayLevels: the number of sublevels shown for various levels.
  • startValue: the start value if the number for various levels.

freesb
